            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>BREVE RECORDATIONIS FACIO EGO <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Martinus">MARTINUS</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">ABBAS</rs> DE <rs key="#Fisheries">PISCARIA</rs> DE AQUA
                        DE <rs key="#Rivers">OSARE</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1" key="#Marquis/duke">Bonifatius</persName> gratia
                        Dei <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux et marhio</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">rendidit</rs> ille duo <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">sepes</rs> de aqua <rs key="#Rivers">Ausert</rs>
                        medietatem de <rs key="#Fish">lamprede et omnes pissces</rs> qui ibi capti
                        sunt quos antea <persName><name ref="Farulfus">Farulfus</name></persName>
                        filio <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Leo">Lei</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatoris</rs> sibi retinebat tunc precepit
                        dux et marchio Bonifatius <persName><name ref="Teudaldus"
                            >Tedaldi</name></persName> filius ad <rs key="#Other_minor_officer"
                            >ministerialem</rs> suum <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Other_minor_officer"><name ref="Hubertus"
                            />Uberto</persName> nomine ut <rs key="#Inquisitio">probaret</rs> per
                        fideles laici nec non et senes illius villule si esset hec sepes de <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71">Sancti Pontiani</orgName> sicut audiebat nam
                        una dierum in mense martio secunda septimana in feria IIII perrexit iste
                        Uberto cum aliis <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">boni viri</rs> ad <rs
                            key="#Villages/settlements">villulam</rs> illam <placeName
                            ref="#places/22"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Marquis/duke"
                            >Flexo</placeName> nomine ubi sunt piscarie ut interrogarent si de
                        monasterio illo fieri deberent medietatem de iste duo sepes et precepit et
                        rogavit qui ibi aderant ut veritatem panderent (…) si vera esset de iste duo
                        piscarie et responderunt omnes una voce dixerunt vera vera sunt domne que
                        audistis et testificamus et iuramus quia medietatem de piscationibus fieri
                        deberent abbatibus qui constituerunt omnes ut per sacramenta probarentur
                        statimque venerunt tres viri fratres consanguinei et Deo timentes in
                        presentia domni illi UBERTI ministeriale de <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Judge"><name ref="Beritius"
                                >Berizi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatoris</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocato</rs> piissimi
                        marchionis <persName><name ref="Bollitius">Bollizio</name></persName> qualem
                        iuravit primus deinde inde <persName><name ref="Bonitius"
                            >Bonatus</name></persName> iuravit secundus tertius <persName><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> finivit sacramenta quod iste
                        duo sepes suptus omnes alias sepes fieri derent omnes pisces propri de
                        fratres monasterii et lamprede quei ibi adpreense erant <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Marquis/duke"
                            >medietatem marhioni et medietatem monasterii</rs> iste sacramenta fuit
                        in presentia UBERTI <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldi</rs> et
                        coram Berizio advocato ibi fuit Farulfus filio Lei iudex (…) <rs
                            key="#Witness">testimonia</rs> multa habemus et hec breve recordationis
                        fieri iusserunt ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Paccus"
                            >Pacio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary #Witness">notario domni imperatoris</rs> interfui <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Alcherius">Alcleri</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Ilditius">Ilditi</name></persName> ibi fuit
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gherardus">Ierardo</name></persName>
                        filio <persName><name ref="Wido">Widi</name></persName> interfui <persName
                            key="#Other_clerics #Witness"><name ref="Gundo">Gunzo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs> ibi fuit <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Drudo">Drudo</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Teudo">Teuzi</name></persName> interfuit <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Ermingo">Ermingoni</name></persName> ibi fuit
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildibrando</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Fraolmus"
                                >Fralmi</name></persName> interfui <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3124">Vallecla</placeName> ibi fuit <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albo/Pane Vetero">Alboni</name> Pane
                            Vetero</persName> interfuit <persName key="#Priests #Witness"><name
                                ref="Rigitius">Rikizo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> ibi fuit <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Izzo">Iczo</name></persName> de Flexo ibi fuit ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Bonitius">Bonati</name></persName> de Flexo ibi
                        fuit. Post hec omnia acta investivimus nos illi piscatores quanto tempore
                        nos placet de decem et VIII lamprede duo debent habere.</ab>
                        </div>
